    {
      "id": "T18",
      "desc": "translate Japanese",
      "called_tool": null,
      "called_tools": [],
      "expected_tool": "translate",
      "expected_tools": null,
      "tool_correct": false,
      "params_correct": false,
      "params_detail": {},
      "score": 0.0,
      "raw_content": "There are several ways to say \"goodbye\" in Japanese, depending on the situation and who you are speaking to:\n\n### 1. The Most Common (General)\n*   **Say\u014dnara (\u3055\u3088\u3046\u306a\u3089):** This is the standard \"goodbye\" taught in textbooks. However, it can sound quite formal or final (like \"farewell\"). It is often used when you won't see the person for a long time or at all.\n\n### 2. Casual (With Friends and Family)\n*   **Ja, ne (\u3058\u3083\u3042\u306d):** \"See ya!\" (Very common among friends).\n*   **Mata ne (\u307e\u305f\u306d):** \"See you later.\"\n*   **Bai bai (\u30d0\u30a4\u30d0\u30a4):** \"Bye-bye.\" (Very casual, used mostly by younger people or in informal settings).\n\n### 3. Business or Formal Situations\n*   **Shitsurei shimasu (\u5931\u793c\u3057\u307e\u3059):** \"Excuse me for being rude.\" This is the standard way to leave an office, hang up the phone, or leave a meeting.\n*   **O-saki ni shitsurei shimasu (\u304a\u5148\u306b\u5931\u793c\u3057\u307e\u3059):** \"Excuse me for leaving before you.\" Use this specifically when you are leaving work while your colleagues are still there.\n\n### 4. Specific Situations\n*   **O-yasumi nasai (\u304a\u3084\u3059\u307f\u306a\u3055\u3044):** \"Goodnight.\" Use this when you are going to bed or leaving someone's house late at night.\n*   **Ittekimasu (\u884c\u3063\u3066\u304d\u307e\u3059):** \"I'm going (and coming back).\" Use this when you are leaving your own home.\n*   **Itterasshai (\u3044\u3063\u3066\u3089\u3063\u3057\u3083\u3044):** \"Please go and come back.\" This is what the people staying home say to the person leaving.\n\n**Summary Tip:** If you are unsure what to use with a friend, **\"Mata ne\"** is almost always a safe and natural choice!",
      "latency_s": 9.53
    },
